-- MOVES-Llyods appoints Theresa Newell as co-head of leveraged credit sales
-- 
-- Fri Dec 12, 2014 11:56AM EST
-- None



Dec 12 (Reuters) - Lloyds Bank Commercial Banking appointed Theresa Newell as managing director and co-head of its leveraged credit sales division.

Newell was most recently head of the high yield credit sales at Lloyds Bank. She will work alongside Paul Osment, co-head of leveraged credit sales and report to Adam Barrett, managing director and head of institutional sales.